<OPENER><SALUTE>SIR,</SALUTE></OPENER>
<P>BY Order of the Weekly Board now &s;itting, I beg Leave to acquaint you, That <GAP DESC="blank"> recommended by you as an [In or Out] Patient, is di&s;charged [Cured] [Relieved] [at his own Reque&s;t,] [Incurable] [Dead] [For Non-Attendance] [For Irregularity]</P>
<CLOSER><SIGNED>Secretary.</SIGNED></CLOSER>
